column16: Nomar Mazara pops out to catcher Roberto Perez in foul territory.
Robinson Chirinos grounds out, shortstop Michael Martinez to first baseman Carlos Santana.
Elvis Andrus lines out sharply to shortstop Michael Martinez.
Junior Lake grounds out softly, second baseman Jose Ramirez to first baseman Carlos Santana.
Justin Smoak homers (9) on a fly ball to right field.    Russell Martin scores.
Troy Tulowitzki pops out to second baseman Jose Ramirez.
Russell Martin singles on a soft line drive to right fielder Tyler Naquin.   Edwin Encarnacion scores.
Michael Saunders flies out to center fielder Abraham Almonte.   Edwin Encarnacion to 3rd.
Edwin Encarnacion doubles (21) on a line drive to left fielder Rajai Davis.   Josh Donaldson scores.
Josh Donaldson doubles (19) on a sharp line drive to left fielder Rajai Davis.
Ezequiel Carrera pops out to third baseman Lonnie Chisenhall.
Darwin Barney flies out to center fielder Abraham Almonte.
Junior Lake lines out sharply to left fielder Rajai Davis.
